overview: Goa Vich Nach Le' (Hindi: गोवा विच नच ले ) is an Indian Hindi-Punjabi music album released by Z-Series. The music album stars Lalit Agarwal, Zuber K Khan, Pooja Puri and Pentali Sen. The album is produced by Lalit Agarwal and lyrics are written by Ashok Punjabi while the music of the album is given by Dilip Sen.
title: Goa Vich Nach Le
